MOST IMMEDIATE
No. 1/34/1/2013-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th June, 2013
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 15th June, 2013:
(i)
Shri C.P. Joshi relinquished the charge of (a) the office of the Minister of Road Transport and
Highways; and (b) the office of the Minister of Railways;
(ii)
Shri Ajay Maken, relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Housing and Urban
Poverty Alleviation; and
(ii)
the Prime Minister assumed the charge of (a) the office of the Minister of Road Transport and
Highways; (b) the office of the Minister of Railways; and (c) the office of the Minister of Housing
and Urban Poverty Alleviation.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 5802
To
Ail Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Deputy Chairman and Members
the Planning
Commission.
(K.L. Sharma)
